snippet.title: Omerta: City of Gangsters 2nd Trailer
snippet.description:
Omerta: City of Gansters is available for pre-orders now: http://j.mp/omerta_gog

Omerta: City of Gangsters, an organized crime simulation that will let you dominate 1930s Atlantic City as a mafia boss, is available for pre-order on GOG.com for only $33.99, which is 15% off the regular price.
